	<h3>Learning Installations</h3>	
	<p>	The Learning Installations group is prototyping a new platform for digitally augmenting printed material and posters. Using low-cost hand held touch pads and object tracking algorithms, this system allows for a virtual window onto the printed material. The touch screen makes visible extra layers of augmented information, superimposed over the printed image. This way, new information can be explored and added to such printed material as maps, photographs, diagrams, and artwork.
	</p>
	
