	<p>Kiteviz is an interactive visualization designed to promote reflection and support collaboration in small groups. It uses a kite flying metaphor to depict group members, their microblogging activities and communication interactions between participants. Kiteviz allows users to identify dynamic patterns of group activity and the relative closeness between members over time.<br /><br />
