	<h3>Soundwalks</h3>
	<p>
	<a href="http://Soundwalks.org/" target="blank">Soundwalks.org</a> is a community website and mobile application dedicated to exploring the world's rich sonic landscape. Analysis of acoustic ecology - how life relates to its environment through sound - can help to explore and provide community understanding for urban planning, maintenance of wildlife preserves, and cultural activity from community events to crime. With Soundwalks, users are able to drag anywhere on a map to hear a continuous soundscape from that area, contribute their own recordings, discuss their environments, and visualize changes in activity over time.<br/><br/>
